# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  News Bot — Environment Variables
#  Copy this file to .env and fill in your values
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
#  You can enable WhatsApp, Telegram, or BOTH at the same time.
#  At least one platform must be configured.
#
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  WHATSAPP (optional)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# WHERE TO SEND NEWS — pick ONE of the 3 options:
#
# Option 1: Your personal WhatsApp number (country code + number, no + or spaces)
WHATSAPP_TARGET=919XXXXXXXXX
#
# Option 2: WhatsApp Group name (case-insensitive, must match exactly)
# WHATSAPP_TARGET=My Cyber News Group
#
# Option 3: WhatsApp Group ID (most reliable — run: npm run list-groups)
# WHATSAPP_TARGET=120363XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX@g.us

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  TELEGRAM (optional)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Step 1: Create a bot at https://t.me/BotFather → /newbot → copy token
# TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=123456789:ABCDefghIJKlmnoPQRstuvWXYz

# Step 2: Set the destination (chat, group, or channel)
#   Personal chat:   123456789          (send any message to the bot first)
#   Group:          -987654321          (add bot to group, send a message)
#   Channel:        @mychannel          (public channel username)
#   Channel ID:     -1001234567890      (private channel — add bot as Admin first)
#
#   Run: npm run list-telegram-chats  to auto-discover your chat IDs
# TELEGRAM_TARGET=@mychannel

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  AI SUMMARIZATION (optional but recommended)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Free Gemini API key from https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
# Without this, the bot uses basic sentence extraction instead
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here
